    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's weird because people always talk about \"hope\" but hope feels like a burden right now. like it's just another thing i have to carry when i'm already so tired. when you talk about \"letting go\" and \"release\"... it sounds almost peaceful. like there's a mercy in just being done with it all. do you think it's wrong to see it that way? to think that maybe there's peace in the end?",
